    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Units of distance in English-speaking countries, equal to 1760 yards or approximately 1609 meters. It is derived from Roman units of distance of 1000 paces, or approximately 1618 yards. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
